<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٣٤١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6542">نَصْرُ بْنُ عَلِيِّ بْنِ نَصْرٍ </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5748">أَبُو أَحْمَدَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4851">أَبِي إِسْحَاقَ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/710">الْأَسْوَدِ بْنِ يَزِيدَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3913">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّ رَسُولَ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَرَأَ ﴿فَهَلْ مِنْ مُدَّكِرٍ﴾ مِثْلَ قِرَاءَةِ الْعَامَّةِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>